At VickSan, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle and protect your information when you use our language learning app.

1. Data Collection
We are committed to providing a safe and secure learning experience, and we want to be transparent with you about the information we collect. VickSan does not collect any personal data. This means we do not gather or store any of the following:

Your name
Your email address
Your phone number
Your physical address
Your payment information
Any other personal information
We do not require you to create an account or share any personal details to use the app.

2. Usage Data and Analytics
While we do not collect personal information, we may collect non-personally identifiable information to improve the appâ€™s functionality and performance. This may include:

Information about how you interact with the app (such as the features you use, your progress, etc.)
Device information (e.g., device type, operating system)
Usage statistics (e.g., how often the app is opened, session length)
This data helps us improve the user experience, identify bugs, and optimize the app for better performance.

Note: This usage data is typically collected through third-party analytics tools. These tools do not collect any personal information about you.

3. Third-Party Services
We may use third-party services, such as Google Analytics, to analyze how users interact with the app. These third parties may collect anonymized information about your use of the app, but they do not collect personal data. For more information about how these third-party services collect and use your data, please review their respective privacy policies.

Google Analytics: Google Privacy Policy
We do not share any personal data with third parties.

4. Security
We take your privacy and security seriously. Since we do not collect any personal data, there is minimal risk in terms of data breaches. However, we implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information, including encryption and secure connections for any third-party services we may use.

5. Children's Privacy
VickSan is intended for users of all ages. However, we do not knowingly collect or solicit any personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete such information from our records.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the effective date of the updated policy will be clearly indicated. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your privacy.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us at:

Email: deutschy.app@gmail.com

By using the VickSan app, you agree to this Privacy Policy. Thank you for trusting us with your learning experience!
